snippet.title: Cave Chaos 2 (Nitrome.com) - Full Gameplay Levels 1-15
snippet.description:
Gameplay of Cave Chaos 2. The sequel of Cave Chaos and in my opinion a very big improvement respect the first one. This sequel has less levels but they are very cool and the graphics improved a lot.
You can play it in: https://www.nitrome.com/html5-games/cavechaos2/#.YLyzfYVxc2w
I hope you like it!
